"tid":2097732,"uid":287422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T04:59:24.000Z","msg":"參軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72eb68d08b01ec0891d6f7e7e4440bed43316617","tid":2097732,"uid":2267,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"7a92e727325c57effb2008b592b2a6f138e11088","tid":2097732,"uid":35814,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"d4a47cfdb39bb6b6f53ab2a0a6b31fe6599cde47","tid":2097732,"uid":2267,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T04:27:55.000Z","msg":"你去過外國生活未？"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T04:46:33.000Z","msg":"我未<br />\n但如果可以做開荒牛或下欄野都唔介意<br />\n自己知自己事<br />\n冇專業技能<br />\n<br />\n大佬呀！<br />\n我難民/移民黎架咋！<br />\n人哋政府正路都顧自己人先啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T05:20:51.000Z","msg":"我就玩過working holiday<br />\n其實只要自己唔介意勞動力工作，喺外國都有好多選擇嘅工。雖然我當年係玩住打工，求鳩其住宿同食，但如果想做得輕鬆啲，有車牌可以做運輸/司機。<br />\n外國亦有好多工廠嘅重複性工作，好多都係以多勞多得形式出糧<br />\n西方國家普遍都係慢生活慢工作，以香港人急促文化係要適應，有時會懷疑人生點解會咁多時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n住宿睇你住城市入面定遠少少？好多人為慳啲會住遠少少，即係交通一兩個鐘左右<br />\n識得個鬼妹，返工自己揸車一程都要差唔多90分鐘，但佢買咗棟別墅式嘅屋連唔知幾千呎嘅花園（唔使200萬港紙）<br />\n代用喺香港，我就住新界區嘅，返工喺市區（九龍），交通閒閒地都60分鐘，我覺得完全無問題。但住市區嘅人，要你搭60分鐘或以上車程返工，一定唔慣同屌晒鬼不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03e781d49ff8ae8759c2ef515db2935c408db273","tid":2097732,"uid":118346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T10:02:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmo